text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: alkisah , ni sebuah kute ( kute neggekhi desa ) megelakh kute kekhan si megelakh ken salah sebuah tanoh alas , kabupaten aceh tenggakhe sendah ende .

free_transl.en: Once upon a time in a town (Red-Gampong, Nagari, village) called Engkeran Town which is one of the regions of Alas Land, which is the district of Southeast Aceh today.
free_transl.id: Alkisah di suatu kuta (Red-Gampong, Nagari, desa), bernama kuta Engkeran yang merupakan salah satu wilayah Tanah Alas, Kabupaten Aceh Tenggara saat ini.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: geluh sekelompok masakhakat si gemakh me gotokhoyong te saling membantu sebuah khut lain ne .

free_transl.en: Lived a group of people who like to work together and help one another.
free_transl.id: Hiduplah sekelompok Masyarakat yang gemar bergotong royong dan saling membantu satu sama lain.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kalak di geluh mecocok tanemen te mejume , ni kakheneken tanoh ne mejile kalihen subukh mebahan hasil panen setiap tahun ne melimpah khuah .

free_transl.en: They make a living by farming and tending the paddy fields, because the very fertile land results in abundant crops every year.
free_transl.id: mereka hidup dengan bercocok tanam dan bersawah, di karenakan tanahnya sangatlah subur membuat hasil panen setiap tahunnya berlimbah ruah.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kute tekhsebut nipinpin oleh sebuah khaje cut si memekhintah ken secakhe tukhun menukhun te tunduk khut kejujukhen se bulan te setiap tahun ne megikhim ken pajak me sultan aceh dakhussalam .

free_transl.en: The town is led by a small king who has ruled for generations and is subject to the honesty of Mbatu Mbulan and annually sends taxes to the Sultan of Aceh Darussalam.
free_transl.id: Kuta tersebut dipimpin oleh seorang raja kecil yang memerintah secara turun temurun dan tunduk pada kejujuran Mbatu Mbulan dan setiap tahunnya mengirimkan pajak ke Sultan Aceh Darussalam.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: ni kisah ken , semenjak menikahi pemain sukhi ne hinge sendah beliau mange kane ni kakhuniai sekalak anak .

free_transl.en: It is said, since marrying his queen until now he has not been blessed with a son.
free_transl.id: Di kisahkan, semenjak menikahi permaisurinya hingga sekarang beliau belum juga dikaruniai  seorang putra.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: hal edi kelok lah membahe ken bagi setekhusne ke khajaen si ni pinpin ne kakhene suku alas kakhene suku si menganut sistem patkhilineal si dape menakhik gakhis ketukhunen akhi pihak laki~laki jadi namin laki~laki aminlah si mehak menekhus ken gakhis ketukhunen te menjadi khaje .

free_transl.en: This is very dangerous for the continuation of the kingdom that is led by him, because the Alas tribe is a tribe that adopts the Patrilineal system which draws a lineage from the male side, so only men are entitled to continue the lineage and become king.
free_transl.id: Hal ini sangatlah berbahaya bagi keberlangsungan kerajaan yang dipimpinnya karena suku Alas adalah suku yang menganut sistem Patrilineal yang mana menarik garis keturunan dari pihak laki-laki, jadi hanya laki-laki sajalah yang berhak melanjutkan garis keturunan dan menjadi raja.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: pade suatu bongi , sang pemain sukhi khaje medikusi khut lakine , " kanda , engo dekah kite mekhumah tangge , nangat khasene adinda memiliki sekalak anak laki~laki ".

free_transl.en: One night, the king's wife discussed with her husband, "Please, we have been married for a long time. I want to have a son."
free_transl.id: ​​Pada Suatu malam, sang permaisuri raja berdiskusi dengan suaminya, “Kanda,,, sudah lama kita berumah tangga, ingin rasanya adinda mempunyai seorang anak laki-laki”

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: benakh adinda , kanda menangkat ken hal si bali , de kelak pagi aku ni tengo allah , te kite endak lot ketukhunen , kanda biakh endak lot nange penekhus kekhajaen ngkekhan ende "

free_transl.en: "Right, dearest, I also want the same thing. If tomorrow I am called by God, and we have no descendants, I am afraid there will be no successor to the Ngkeran kingdom."
free_transl.id: “benar adindaku,kanda juga menginginkan hal yang sama, jika kelak esok aku di panggil Allah, dan kita tidak punya keturunan, kanda takut tidak ada lagi penerus kerajaan Ngkeran ini”.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: bongi ge suntuk khaje te pemain sukhine medikusi gedang .

free_transl.en: All night the king and his queen had a long discussion.
free_transl.id: Semalam suntuk Raja dan permaisurinya berdiskusi panjang.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: te sohlah pade titik jump , pepagi ne kalaki tekhus memulungken kekhine ahli nujum ( dukun ) si mejile lot ni selukhuh tanoh alas , kakho te belang kejekhen , namun nihil kekhine usahe edi sie~sie telat buah ahli nujum pe si mampu memekhe ken jawaben sikal kegelisahen sepasang suami istekhi edi .

free_transl.en: And until the meeting time, tomorrow morning they will gather all the best fortune-tellers (Shamans) in all the Alas, Karo, and Blangkejeren lands, but all that effort was in vain and there was not even one fortune-teller who was able to give an answer for the anxieities of the husband and wife.
free_transl.id: Dan sampailah pada titik temu, besok pagi mereka akan mengumpulkan semua ahli Nujum (Dukun) terbaik yang ada diseluruh tanah Alas, Karo dan Blangkejeren, namun Nihil semua usaha itu sia-sia tak ada satu ahli nujum pun yang mampu memberikan jawaban akan kegelisahan sepasang suami-istri ini.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: hampikh putus ase , doe te usahe engo kalaki due ne melaku ken kekhine .

free_transl.en: Almost giving up out of despair, they prayed and they tried everything together.
free_transl.id: Hampir putus asa, doa dan usaha telah mereka berdua lakukan semuanya.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: sohlah pade suatu wakhi tebege oleh sekalak tentang kehebaten sekalak jeme gukhu mebelin sekalak jeme dukun hebat , si tading ni singkil si kehebaten ne malot ni khagu ken nange ni daekhah ne .

free_transl.en: Until one day, a person heard about the greatness of the Master Teacher, a Great Shaman, who lived in the Singkil area, whose greatness was not doubted in his area.
free_transl.id: sampai lah pada suatu hari terdengar oleh seorang tentang kehebatan seorang Guru Mbelin seorang Dukun Hebat, yang tinggal di Singkil yang kehebatanya tak diragukan lagi di daerahnya.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: bekhite kesokhokhen dukun edi ni dapet akhi pakhe pedagang alas si melayakh me singkil men jadi ken hasil deleng bage gule pole , ketang buah~buahen te balikne kalaki membabe hasil bumi akhi pesisikh bage sikhe , ikan laut , kekhang te sebagene .

free_transl.en: The shaman's famous news was obtained from Alas traders who sailed to Singkil peddling forest products such as palm sugar, rattan, and fruit, and they traded those for produce from the coast such as salt, sea fish, and shellfish, etc.
free_transl.id: berita kesohoran dukun itu didapat dari para pedagang Alas yang berlayar ke Singkil menjajakan hasil hutan seperti gula aren, rotan buah-buahan dan sebaliknya mereka membawa hasil bumi dari pesisir seperti garam, ikan laut, kerang dll.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: memege kabakh edi mebahan ate khaje gembikhe kalihen , te niat khaje enggo bulet kalihen pepagi ne beliau khut pe main sukhine te pepige pengawal kekhajaen ne bekhangkat me singkil , melewati lawe alas khut nangkih bungki si milik layakh .

free_transl.en: Hearing this news made the king's heart very happy, and the king's desire was very clear that tomorrow was the day that he and the queen and some of his royal guards would go to Singkil, via the Alas River on a sailboat.
free_transl.id: Mendengar kabar itu membuat hati raja sangat gembira, dan Niat Raja sudah sangat bulat besok hari beliau bersama permaisuri dan beberapa pengawal kerajaannya berangkat ke Singkil, melalui Sungai Alas dengan menaiki perahu yang memiliki layar.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: pitu wakhi pitu bongi dekah ne untuk soh me singkil si tading ni pesisikh .

free_transl.en: It took seven days and seven nights to get to the Singkil coast.
free_transl.id: tujuh hari tujuh malam lamanya untuk sampai ke Singkil yang berada di pesisir.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: sesoh ne ni singkil khombongen khaje malet susah mendapat ken ketadingen sang gukhu , kakhene enggo bue jeme luakh akhi khoh me singkil amin hendak me daun me sang gukhu .

free_transl.en: Arriving at Singkil, the King's entourage had no difficulty finding where the Master Teacher lived, because many people from outside the area came to Singkil to seek treatment from the Master Teacher.
free_transl.id: Sesampainya di Singkil rombongan Raja ini tidak susah mendapatkan kediaman sang Guru, karena sudah banyak orang dari luar datang ke Singkil Cuma hendak berobat ke sang Guru.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: ni khumah gukhu mbelin kalakdi medaun khut tekun te sabakh , sang khaje me matuhi kekhine pesakhaten si ni pido oleh dukun mebane .

free_transl.en: In the home of the Master Teacher, they sought treatment with diligence and patience, and the king complied with all the requirements requested by the Shaman for him.
free_transl.id: Dirumah Guru Mbelin mereka berobat dengan tekun dan sabar, sang raja mematuhi segala persyaratan yang diminta oleh dukun kepadanya.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: wakhi setekhusne melalu soh pade wakhi enem puluh due , sang gukhu mbelin mecekhok " balik lah kenin , yakinlah bahwe setahun si sikel khoh bekhumu enggo memangku sekalak anak laki~laki ".

free_transl.en: The days continued to pass until the 62nd day, when the Master Teacher said, "Go home, you can rest assured that in the coming year your wife will hold a boy child."
free_transl.id: Hari terus berlalu sampai pada hari ke-62, Sang Guru Mbelin berkata “pulanglah kalian,,, yakinlah bahwa setahun yang akan datang istrimu telah memangku seorang anak laki-laki”.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: khut mebelin ate te penuh hakhapen balik lah kalaki me tanoh alas khut medalan kiding memengketi nangkihe datas tanoh kakho .

free_transl.en: With encouragement and hope they returned to the Alas Land on foot entering the Karo highlands.
free_transl.id: Dengan berbesar hati dan penuh harapan pulanglah mereka ke Tanah Alas dengan berjalan kaki memasuki dataran tinggi Tanah Karo.

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: selame sang khaje tonge ni singkil , pengulu mude lah si mekhupe ken engek kandung akhi khaje ngkekhan .

free_transl.en: While the king was in Singkil, Pengulu Mude was the younger brother of King Ngkeran.
free_transl.id: Selama sang Raja berada di Singkil, Pengulu Mude Lah yang merupakan adik kandung dari Raja Ngkeran

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: sang khaje malet nange balik kakhene enggo betah ni tanoh singkil atau nasip naas khombongen khaje jumpe penamun ni pedalanen menuju balik me tanoh alas .

free_transl.en: The king will not return because he has settled in the land of Singkil or the king's entourage has had bad fate and has been ambushed on his way back to the Alas Land.
free_transl.id: sang raja takkan kembali lagi karena sudah betah di tanah Singkil atau nasib naas rombongan raja bertemu penyamun di perjalanan menuju kembali ke Tanah Alas,

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: belin hakhapen pengulu mude .

free_transl.en: The hopes of Penghulu Mude were big.
free_transl.id: besar harapan Penghulu Mude

text_title: 1 - Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: hal edi tekhjadi si ape secakhe otomatis anak mahkota amin lah iye si mehak menjadi khaje setekhus ne menginget sang khaje malot memiliki ke tukhunen si sah .

free_transl.en: It so happened to be he was the only one entitled to the crown to become the next king, since the king did not have any legitimate offspring.
free_transl.id: Hal itu terjadi yang mana secara otomatis putra mahkota hanyalah dia yang berhak menjadi raja selanjutnya mengingat sang raja tidak memilik keturunan yang sah.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: namun pengkikhaen pengulu mude meleset .

free_transl.en: But Pengulu Mude's understanding of the situation was far from the truth.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: sang khaje te bekhune engo balik me kute ne ni kekhan khut wajah mesekhi~sekhi te siap menjabut saat~saat si nitimai soh .

free_transl.en: The king and his wife had returned to the town in Engkeran with beaming faces and were ready to welcome the expected time to arrive.
free_transl.id: Sang raja dan istri telah kembali ke Kuta-nya di Engkeran dengan wajah berseri-seri dan siap menyambut saat-saat yang dinantikan tiba.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: pige bulan kemudian bekhune , mengandung bage si ni kateken si dukun .

free_transl.en: A few months later the wife was carrying a child like what the shaman had said.
free_transl.id: Beberapa bulan kemudian istrinya mengandung seperti yang dikatakan si dukun.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: senanglah kikhene sang khaje memege kabakh bahwe sang bekhune enggo mengandung sekalak anak .

free_transl.en: The king was so happy to hear the news that his wife was pregnant with a child.
free_transl.id: Senanglah kiranya sang raja mendengar kabar bahwa sang istri sudah mengandung seorang anak.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kabakh mengandung ne bekhu sang khaje ni sambut suke~cite oleh selukhuh khakyat ni kekhajaen cut edi .

free_transl.en: News of the king's wife's pregnancy  was welcomed with joy by all of the people in the small kingdom.
free_transl.id: Kabar mengandungnya istri sang raja disambut suka-cita oleh seluruh rakyat di kerajaan kecil ini.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kekhine khut kegembikhen , namun malet bagi pengulu mude .

free_transl.en: Everyone was filled with excitement, but not for Pengulu Mude.
free_transl.id: Semua larut dengan kegembiraan, namun tidak bagi Pengulu mude.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: niat ate ne menjadi khaje sikel sulit tekhcape khut kehadikhen sekalak anak akhi sang khaje .

free_transl.en: His desire to become the king would be very difficult to fulfill with the presence of a child from the king.
free_transl.id: Niat hati ingin menjadi raja akan sangat sulit tercapai dengan kehadiran seorang anak dari sang raja.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kane munculah niat jahat akhi pengulu mude untuk menyingkikhken calon bayi sang khaje khut memido sekalak ahli nujum untuk mebahan sebuah tekhadep bayi si ni angap oleh pengulu mude sebage pembabe bencane bagi geluh ne .

free_transl.en: Then came Penghulu Mude's evil desire to get rid of the future baby of the king by asking a fortune-teller to do something about the baby that Pengulu Mude considered to be the cause of his life's disaster.
free_transl.id: Maka muncullah niat jahat dari Penghulu Mude untuk menyingkirkan calon bayi sang raja dengan meminta seorang ahli nujum untuk berbuat sesuatu terhadap bayi yang dianggap oleh pengulu mude sebagai pembawa bencana bagi hidupnya.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " wahai tukang nujum bendelah kite me khumah khaje .

free_transl.en: "Hi fortune-teller, let us go to the king's house.
free_transl.id: “Wahai tukang nujum marilah kita ke rumah raja.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: aku sikel nimai kao mecekhok tebe sang khaje , bahwe anak si kelak sikel lahekh edi adalah anak si amin membabe balepetake te membabe semsakhe ni negekhi ende ."

free_transl.en: I want you to tell the king that the child who will be born is a child who will only bring disaster and misery to this country..."
free_transl.id: Aku ingin nanti engkau berkata kepada sang raja, bahwa anak yang kelak akan lahir itu adalah anak yg hanya membawa malapetaka dan membawa sengsara di negeri ini..."

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: pengulu mude memekhe ken akhah tebe dukun tekhsebut .

free_transl.en: Pengulu mude gave those directions to the fortune-teller.
free_transl.id: Pengulu mude memberikan arahan kepada dukun tersebut.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " pak dukun si hebat , de lah khencane edi mekhasil , sehinge anak khaje edi nahan ne tekhsingkikh , te aku sikel menjadi khaje kelak kao sikel aku angkat menjadi penasehat kekhajaen .

free_transl.en: "Sir, the great shaman...if this plan is successful, so that the king's son will be eliminated, and I will become king later, I will appoint you as the royal adviser."
free_transl.id: "Pak dukun yang hebat… kalau lah rencana ini berhasil, sehingga anak raja ini nantinya tersingkir, dan aku akan menjadi raja kelak engkau akan aku angkat menjadi penasehat kerajaan."

free_transl.id: “menurut penerawangan yang hamba dapati dari datu muyang kita, kelahiran anak tuanku raja hanya akan membawa bala petaka dinegeri kita ini, negeri yang sudah tuanku pimpin bertahun-tahun dan menjadikannya makmur, aman, dan hasil bumi yang tetap melimpah ruah.

orig_line: wakhi demi wakhi enggo melalu soh lah pade bulan ke~siwah bage si enggo ni pekikheken lahikhlah sekalak anak bayi laki~laki si sehat , te ganteng , te oleh uwakne iye ni ekhe gelakh si layakh , ni kakheneken bungki si membabe uwak te amek ne me singkil mengane ken layakh sebagae salah sebuah pegekhoken ne .

free_transl.en: Day after day passed until the 9th month, and as  expected, a healthy and handsome baby boy was born. And his father gave him the name Si Layakh, because of the boat that brought his father and mother to Singkil a long time ago using the sail as its power.
free_transl.id: Hari demi hari telah berlalu sampai lah pada bulan ke-9 seperti yang telah diperkirakan lahirlah seorang anak bayi laki-laki yang sehat, dan tampan, dan oleh ayahnya dia diberi nama Si Layakh, di karenakan perahu yang membawa ayah dan ibunya ke Singkil tempo dulu menggunakan layar sebagai salah satu penggeraknya.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.

free_transl.en: News of his good looks and the birth of the king of Engkeran's baby reached the ears of the ruler of Natam, who was none other than the uncle of Si Layakh himself.
free_transl.id: Berita ketampanan dan lahirnya bayi sang raja engkeran sampai juga pada telinga penguasa dari Natam, yang tak lain adalah paman Si layakh sendiri,

free_transl.en: So the ruling party from Natam came to see the handsome baby Si Layakh.
free_transl.id: maka datanglah rombongan penguasa dari Natam itu ke ngkran melihat langsung bayi si layakh yang tampan.

orig_line: se enggo mekhumukh lebih kukhang lebih waluh belas tahun , kegantengen si layakh semakin jelas ni banding ken khut pemude~pemude lain ne ni tanoh alas edi .

free_transl.en: After he was about 18 years old, Si Layakh's good looks, intelligence, and prowess were increasingly clear compared to other youths in the Alas Land.
free_transl.id: Setelah berusia lebih kurang lebih 18 tahun, ketampanan, kecerdikkan dan kegagahan Si Layakh semakin jelas di bandingkan dengan pemuda-pemuda lainnya di Tanah Alas ini.

text_title: 2- Pengulu Mude
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kekhine nakkhu te okhang tue kalihen beliu ate ne memiliki si layakh menjadi laki atau pemain kalakdi , endak tekhkecuali khut bekhu dinam , anak khu akhi khakyat penguase natam , mame si layakh .

free_transl.en: All the girls and the parents were ready in their hearts to receive Si Layakh as their husband or son-in-law, and that did not exclude Bru Dinam, the daughter of the people of the ruling of Natam, Si Layakh's uncle.
free_transl.id: Semua gadis dan orang tua sangat besar hatinya memiliki Si Layakh menjadi suami atau menantu mereka, tak terkecuali dengan Bru Dinam, anak gadis dari rakyat penguasa Natam, paman Si Layakh.

text_title: 3- Bekhu Dinam

orig_line: kegembikhen mengato tubuh mekembang ne sang anak akhi wakhi me wakhi seketike takkala sang khaje suatu wakhi mengato tule khut kae si ni kate ken oleh ahli nujum tempo die mengenai anjamen malepetake te bahaye si sikel menimpe khaje te negekhi tanoh alas edi .

free_transl.en: The excitement of seeing the child's growth and development suddenly disappeared one day when the king recalled what the fortune-teller had said about the threat of disaster and danger that would befall the king and the Alas land.
free_transl.id: Kegembiraan melihat tumbuh dan berkembangnya sang anak dari hari ke hari sirna seketika tatkala sang raja suatu hari teringat kembali dengan apa yang dikatakan oleh si ahli Nujum tempo dulu mengenai ancaman mala petaka dan bahaya yang akan menimpa raja dan negeri tanah Alas ini.

text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.

free_transl.en: Si Layakh should have been killed when he was born, but Si Layakh's mother pleaded to the king so that little Si Layakh would not be put to death that day.
free_transl.id: Seharusnya Silayakh sudah dibunuh semenjak Ia dilahirkan, namun ibu Si layakh bermohon pada sang raja agar si kecil Layakh untuk tidak di bunuh hari itu juga.

free_transl.id: biarkan adinda yang merawat Silayar untuk beberapa tahun ini sampai ia dewasa dan cukup umur untuk bisa mempertahankan dirinya sendiri kelak.

text_title: 3- Bekhu Dinam
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: sohlah tebe meumukh waluh belas tahun cukuplah khase sang khaje umukh si layakh untuk dikhine khut bekhat sang khaje memekhintah ken anak ne untuk menading ken amek , khumah te tanoh kelahekhen ne untuk menjage kobo ni deleng belantakhe sendikhi khut waktu si endak ni jumpai mase ne .

free_transl.en: When the boy was 18 years old, the king felt Si Layakh was old enough to defend himself, with heaviness the king ordered his son to leave his mother, home, and land of his birth to wander in the wilderness alone for an unspecified amount of time.
free_transl.id: Sampailah pada usia 18 tahun cukuplah rasa sang raja umur Si Layakh untuk menjaga dirinya, dengan berat sang raja memerintahkan anaknya untuk meninggalkan ibu, rumah dan tanah kelahirannya untuk mengembala kobo (Red-Kerbau) di hutan belantara seorang diri dengan waktu yang tak ditentukan masanya.

text_title: 3- Bekhu Dinam
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: sang amek tangis te mencube mekhayu lakine kane ucapen laki ne nemu ni takhik balik te malet sukhung ni cakheken menginget si layakh endak sangub menahan sekalak dikhi ni deleng malet bantuen ise pe , namun sang khaje tetap pade pendikhien ne kane mengasing ken sang anak se mate wayang me deleng belantakhe .

free_transl.en: His mother cried and tried to persuade her husband so that he would take back his words and his orders would not be carried out keeping in mind that Si Layakh would not be able to survive alone in the wilderness without anyone's help, but the king held his stance to exile his only son into the wilderness.
free_transl.id: Sang ibu menangis dan mencoba merayu suaminya agar ucapan suaminya dapat ditarik kembali dan tidak jadi dilaksanakan mengingat Si Layakh tidak akan mampu bertahan seorang diri di hutan tanpa bantuan siapapun, namun sang raja tetap pada pendiriannya untuk mengasingkan sang anak semata wayangnya ke hutan belantara.

free_transl.id: Kabar pengasingan terhadap si layakh sampai jua ke telinga pamannya di Natam, maka diutuslah impalnya Bru dinam ke Ngkran untuk menjumpai Si layakh dan membawanya ke Natam.

text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.

orig_line: " izin ken hambe , tuan penguase lelukhuh tanoh natam , untuk membantu ," si layakh sitok dempik te sitok mebahan suasane menjadi lebuh te sunyi se sikel kalakdi menggangap aneh te khemeh khut kekuaten si ni miliki belagakh dengkil te compang camping edi .

free_transl.en: "Allow your servant, master of the whole land of Natam, to help..." Si Layakh cried out a little and suddenly made the tone of the situation become empty and quiet as if they considered the power possessed by the filthy and tattered youth to be strange and trivial.
free_transl.id: “Izinkan hamba, tuan penguasa seluruh tanah Natam, untuk membantu..”‎‎Si Layakh sedikit berteriak dan sontak membuat suasana menjadi sepi dan sunyi seakan mereka menganggap aneh dan remeh dengan kekuatan yang dimiliki pemuda dekil dan compang-camping itu.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " silah ken anak mude " mame si layakh pe malot menandai bekhe ne khut mejile kakhene tekhahikh kali iye jumpe khut layakh saat si layakh melaku ken khitanen .

free_transl.en: "Please do, young person!" Si Layakh's uncle also did not recognize his nephew very well because the last time he met with Si Layakh was when he was doing a circumcision.
free_transl.id: “Silahkan anak muda!” Paman si layakh juga tidak mengenali keponakkannya dengan baik karena terakhir kali ia berjumpa dengan layakh saat si layakh melakukan khitanan.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: khut sitok mebace due me bagas lawe si iye pido , si layakh meyikhamken lawe edi me selukhuh tihang pekhtame khumah , te ajaib khut nahang ne si layakh khut sekalak dikhi mengangkat tihang edi tanpa bantuen kalak lain , khut pekhistiwe edi mebahan kekhine penduduk takjub te mesokhat gembikhe .

free_transl.en: By a little recitation of the mantra in the water he requested, Si Layakh splashed the water all over the main pillar of the house, and miraculously, Si Layakh raised the pole alone without the help of anyone else, by this event all the citizens were amazed and cheered happily.
free_transl.id: Dengan sedikit membaca mantra ke dalam air yang ia minta, Si layakh menyiramkan air tersebut ke seluruh tiang utama rumah, dan ajaib dengan entengnya Si layakh seorang diri mengangkat tiang tersebut tanpa bantuan orang lain, dengan peristiwa tersebut membuat semua penduduk takjub dan bersorak gembira.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " isekah gekhangen dikhimu wahai anak pemude ?"

free_transl.en: "Who are you, young man?"
free_transl.id: “Siapakah gerangan dirimu wahai anak muda?”

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh

free_transl.en: Asked the ruler of Natam, amazed by the supernatural power of Si Layakh.
free_transl.id: Tanya Penguasa Natam keheranan dengan kesaktian Si Layakh.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " hambe tuan ku , si layakh pengembale kobo akhi deleng engekhan ..."

free_transl.en: "My lord's servant, Si Layakh the cow shepherd from the jungle of Engkran..."
free_transl.id: “Hamba tuanku, Si Layakh Pengembala kerbau dari Hutan engkran...”

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " kao adalah bekhe ku si engo dekah aku gakham~gakhami bendelah nak , tebe khut bajumu ...!"

free_transl.en: "You are my nephew that I have been searching for, come here, son, why are your clothes...!"
free_transl.id: “Kau adalah keponakkanku yang sudah lama aku cari-cari, kemarilah nak, kenapa dengan bajumu....!

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: suasana mekhiyum menabini kendukhi si hakhus ne wakhi edi amin kegembikhe en bagi selukhuh penduduk natam ni tambah khase mele akhi keluakhge kekhajaen ngkhan khut tege mepeluah anggote keluakhge ne telantakh ni deleng mejuang geluh sendikhien .

free_transl.en: The air of emotion enveloping the festivities that should have been that day was joy to all the citizens of Natam plus the shame of the royal family of Ngkran who showed that they had the heart to let a family member be displaced in the forest to struggle to live alone.
free_transl.id: Suasana haru menyelimuti kenduri yang seharusnya hari itu adalah kegembiraan bagi seluruh penduduk Natam ditambah rasa malu dari keluarga kerajaan Ngkran yang dengan tega membiarkan anggota keluarganya terlantar dihutan berjuang hidup sendirian

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: keluakhge kekhajaen ngkhan mebongi ni natam pepige wakhi untuk menghokhmati penguase natam .

free_transl.en: The Ngkran royal family spent the night in Natam a few days in honor of the ruler of Natam.
free_transl.id: Keluarga kerajaan Ngkran bermalam di Natam beberapa hari untuk menghormati penguasa Natam,

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: laus wakhine , wakhi ke~4 bekhangkat lah khombongen khaje ngkhan untuk balik mekhumah kalakdi .

free_transl.en: In the morning, on the fourth day, King Ngkran's entourage departed to return to their homes.
free_transl.id: pagi harinya, hari ke-4 berangkatlah rombongan raja Ngkran untuk kembali ke rumah mereka.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: ikhing~ikhingen khaje ngkhan gendang kalihen , khut posisi tekhadep adalah khaje khut pemain sukhine te ni tekhusi khut ninik pakcik te makcik sang khaje te kane selikh~selikh khaje bakhulah ni paling belakang khombongen medalan pengulu mude khut si layakh .

free_transl.en: King Ngkran's convoy was very long, with the leading position being the king and his queen, and was followed by the older women, the king's uncle and aunt and also the concubines of the king. At the rear of the group Pengulu Mude and Si Layakh were walking.
free_transl.id: Iring-iringan raja Ngkran sangatlah panjang, dengan posisi terdepan adalah raja dan permaisurinya, dan di lanjuti dengan Nenek, pakcik dan makcik sang raja dan juga selir-selir raja barulah di paling belakang rombongan berjalan Pengulu Mude bersama  Si layakh.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: ate pengulu mude mulai cemekh tule khut kehadikh en sikel menjadi saingene menjadi khaje setekhusene , kane timbulah niat jahat ne untuk mengekhi ken bekhene wakhi edi kane .

free_transl.en: Pengulu Mude's heart began to worry again about his nephew being there and becoming his rival to become the next king, so an evil desire arose to finish off his nephew that day.
free_transl.id: Hati pengulu mude mulai cemas kembali dengan kehadiran keponakkannya akan menjadi saingannya menjadi raja selanjutnya, maka timbullah niat jahatnya untuk menghabisi keponakkanya hari itu juga.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: tepat ni daekhah pulau biang si khate dalane si ni tekhuh ne mengalikh lawe akhi pedelengen belang lawe ne 4~5 metekh .

free_transl.en: Right in the Pulo Biang area, the route is hilly, and there are small wooden bridges (about 4-5 meters wide) that have flowing river water from the mountains under them.
free_transl.id: Tepat di daerah Pulo Biang yang rute jalannya berbukit-bukit, dan terdapat titi terbuat dari kayu yang dibawahnya mengalir air Sungai dari pegunungan lebar sungainya 4-5 meter.

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: mekhase kondisi te waktu engo tepat , ni popoklah sang bekhe akhi pudi khut balok kayu khut pengulu mude .

free_transl.en: Feeling the conditions and the timing were right,  the nephew was hit from behind with a wooden block by Pengulu mude.
free_transl.id: Merasa Kondisi dan waktu sudah tepat, dipukullah sang keponakkan dari belakang dengan balok kayu oleh pengulu mude,

text_title: 5 - The Supernatural Power of Si Layakh // 5 - Kesaktian Si Layakh
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: tekhus iye mendabuh ken badan si layakh me lawe si lawene mekhiyut ni lawe alas .

free_transl.en: Then he dropped his body into the river where the water flows into the Alas River.
free_transl.id: lalu ia menjatuhkan tubuh si layakh ke Sungai yang airnya bermuara di Sungai Alas.

words.word_gloss: to be the mouth of a river

free_transl.en: The King of Natam's family had just begun to enjoy the niceties of having a new home, a very large and beautiful house compared to other houses.
free_transl.id: Keluarga Raja Natam baru saja menikmati suasana rumah baru, rumah yang sangat megah dibandingkan rumah-rumah lainnya,

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile

orig_line: namun keyamanen khumah bakhu edi tekhusik khut dempiken~dempiken pakhau akhi sahung khumah .

free_transl.en: But the comfort of the new house was disrupted by the hoarse screams from the roof of the house.
free_transl.id: namun kenyamanan rumah baru itu terusik dengan teriakan-teriakan parau dari atap rumah.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: se engo ni ato me sahung khumah tekhyate engo cindekh tegak sebuah manuk keluki delaki dempik~dempik kekhas se sikel me mekhe sebuah petande kabakh malot mejile .

free_transl.en: After looking at the roof of the house, it turned out that there was a male eagle standing upright and screaming loudly as if giving a sign of bad news.
free_transl.id: Setelah diliat ketap rumah ternyata telah berdiri tegak seekor burung elang jantan berteriak-teriak keras seakan memberi suatu petanda kabar buruk.

words.word_gloss: to be regarded as a sign

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile

orig_line: enggo kabakh edi akhi dape asal ne .

free_transl.en: Where did that news come from?
free_transl.id: sudah kabar itu dari mana asalnya.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: " kabakh malot mejile kae si sedang ni ekhe etoh oleh mu wahai keluki ?"

free_transl.en: "What bad news is being told by the eagle?"
free_transl.id: “Kabar buruk apa yang sedang diberitahukan oleh mu wahai elang?”

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: bekhu dinam sikel mencube menpelehjemah ken sendikhi maksud akhi si keluki mulai muncul uwas~uwas ni ate ne tekhjadi sebuah khut khombongen khaje ngkhan kakhene ke ekhohen keluki edi dekah semase khombongen belin edi menadingken tanoh natam .

free_transl.en: Bru Dinam herself, as if trying to translate what th eagle was saying, had anxiety rise in her heart that something had happened to the king of Ngkran's entourage because the eagle came shortly after the large group left the land of Natam.
free_transl.id: Bru dinam seakan mencoba menterjemahkan sendiri maksud dari sang elang, mulai muncul was-was dihatinya telah terjadi sesuatu dengan rombongan raja ngkran karena kedatangan elang ini tak lama selepas rombongan besar itu meninggalkan tanah natam.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.

free_transl.en: So, a small patrol from the Natam kingdom went to pursue King Ngkran's entourage.
free_transl.id: Maka, menyusullah sekelompok kecil pengawal kerajaan Natam untuk menyusul rombongan Raja Ngkran.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.

free_transl.en: Right when they arrived at Pulo Biang they saw that in a chasm there was a human figure lying in it that looked lifeless.
free_transl.id: Tepat saja sesampainya di Pulo Biang tampak dari bawah jurang sesosok manusia yang tergeletak sepertinya sudah tak bernyawa lagi.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.

free_transl.en: So to ascertain who the person was, one of the patrol men went down to take a look, and it turned out to be Si Layakh was the one that they found.
free_transl.id: Maka untuk memastikan siapa manusia itu maka turunlah salah-satu pengawal melihat langsung, dan ternyata Si Layakh lah yang mereka dapati.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: napos ne me engah engah te deyat nadi ne se sikel~sikel bene te balik megekhot .

free_transl.en: He was breathing heavily and his pulse seemed to disappear and return again.
free_transl.id: Nafasnya ter-engah engah dan denyut nadinya seakan-akan hilang dan kembali berdetak.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kane ni babelah tubuh ne se engo geluh si layakh me natam , te ni dauni oleh tabit dukun mentakh .

free_transl.en: So the body of the half-living Si Layakh was broght to Natam, and Tabib Tengku Putih tried to treat him.
free_transl.id: Maka dibawalah tubuh setengah hidup Si Layakh ke Natam, dan di coba diobati oleh Tabib Tengku Putih.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: biase ne jeme si mengalami pekhistiwe demikian pakhah edi malot mampu nange untuk geluh namun tuhan mekehendak lain .

free_transl.en: Usually people who experience this severe of an event will no longer be able to survive but God said otherwise.
free_transl.id: Biasanya orang yang mengalami peristiwa sedemikian parah ini takkan mampu lagi untuk bertahan hidup namun tuhan berkata lain.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: si layakh tonge nemu metahan te mulai jahan jakh pulih tule .

free_transl.en: Si Layakh survived and began to slowly recover.
free_transl.id: Si Layakh masih bisa bertahan dan mulai berlahan-lahan pulih kembali.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: untuk se mentakhe waktu iye tetap ni natam , tanoh kekuasaen mame ne ni adih iye sikel ni lindungi akhi segale acamen .

free_transl.en: For the time being he remained in Natam, the land of his uncle's authority where he would be protected from all other threats.
free_transl.id: Untuk sementara waktu ia tetap di Natam, tanah kekuasaan pamannya disana ia akan dilindungi dari segala ancaman.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: memege kabakh bahwe si layakh tonge geluh , pengulu mude mekhase ngekhi kane mengato bebekhe ne si bage memiliki nawe , 1000 nawe ne iye .

free_transl.en: Hearing the news that Si Layakh was still alive, Pengulu Mude was horrified to see that his nephew seemed to have 1000 lives.
free_transl.id: Mendengar kabar bahwa Si Layakh masih hidup, Pengulu Mude merasa ngeri juga melihat keponakkannya yang seperti memiliki nyawa 1000.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: engo mencube pigekali pekhcubaen memunuh namun kekhi ne nihil .

free_transl.en: In fact he had tried several assassination attempts but all were to no avail.
free_transl.id: Nyatanya dia sudah mencoba beberapa kali percobaan pembunuhan namun semuanya nihil.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: mungkin pekhencane en ne amin si mange ni susun mejile , pengulu mude mencube meyakin ken dikhi .

free_transl.en: Maybe his planning was just not done well, Pengulu Mude tried to convince himself.
free_transl.id: Mungkin perencanaannya saja yang belum tersusun rapi, pengulu mude mencoba meyakinkan diri.

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: kane ni susunlah sebuah kiasat licik te keji untuk benakh~benakh memunuh bekhene sendikhi kane laus lah pengulu mude me khaje ngkran , abang ne sendikhi untuk bekhangkat menukokh pige~pige kobo .

free_transl.en: Then a devious and vicious strategy was made to actually kill his own nephew, then Pengulu Mude would say goodbye to the king of Ngkran, his own brother, to go to Blangkejeren, the land of the Gayo people to buy some Kobo (red-Buffalo).
free_transl.id: Maka disusunlah suatu siasat licik dan keji untuk benar-benar membunuh keponakkannya sendiri, maka pamitlah Pengulu Mude kepada Raja Ngkran, abangnya sendiri untuk berangkat ke Blangkejeren, tanahnya orang Gayo untuk membeli beberapa Kobo (Red-Kerbau).

text_title: 6 - Not Good News // 6 - Kabakh Malot Mejile
text_comment: This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.
orig_line: namun iye malot me cekhite ken tebe sang khaje bahwe si layakh khut khut  ne me belangkejekhen .

free_transl.en: But he did not tell the king that Si Layakh came with him to Blangkejeren.
